         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 4063, recto: (1) Pasemis, son of Pamonthes, son of [Meswer], has paid to (2) the bank of the northern houses of (3) the silver of poll of year 33 in Jeme, (4) 4 staters. Likewise, for the bath (tax) of year 33, (5) 1 kite. Written in year [33], Mesore 27.</ab>
